{"type": "article", "id": 56131, "title": "Nike 力排众议上线争议广告，微信开设“情绪饮料”快闪店｜乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人相关的一切", "date": "2018-09-06T04:17:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29, "name": "Top 15"}, {"id": 3934, "name": "NFL"}, {"id": 1036, "name": "耐克"}, {"id": 1437, "name": "腾讯"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 50, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180906115109zDQAC7nPIuRVqSB2.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p><a href=\"http://cn.fashionnetwork.com/news/mac-mei-ke-xuan-bu-zhang-yi-xing-cheng-wei-pin-pai-zhong,1009807.html#.W5CM1pMzbfY\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>雅诗兰黛旗下品牌 MAC 宣布张艺兴成为品牌中国首位代言人</b></a>，在全球范围内，MAC 还与 Rihanna、Ariana Grande 等音乐人有过合作。再加上此前的黄子韬、鹿晗，这已经是本周第三位男星出任美妆/护肤品牌代言人。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906101757eKQoAGqDOcUbvCk8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.463768\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>值得一提的 Case</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.espn.com/nfl/story/_/id/24586190/nike-run-colin-kaepernick-ad-nfl-opener-thursday\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>尽管引发了抵制活动甚至股价震荡，Nike 依然选择在今天 NFL 常规赛中播出 Colin Kaepernick 出演的新广告。</b></a>这位前 NFL 四分卫因为激进的政治表达引发联盟球员效仿，目前已经失业超过一年。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.espn.com/nfl/story/_/id/24586190/nike-run-colin-kaepernick-ad-nfl-opener-thursday\" rel=\"nofollow\">根据 ESPN 报道</a>，包括与 Nike 有赞助协议的 NFL，以及其他零售商、合作伙伴此前都没有被告知将在广告中使用 Kaepernick。</p><p class=\"\">选用争议人物是 Nike 营销的常见手法，这也是耐克标语&nbsp;Just do it 30 周年广告计划的一部分。<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/56113.html?share_from=app\">该事件的具体细节可参考 9 月 5 日“乙方日报”栏目的更新。</a></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=d0778fp84bo\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/38387.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>百事发布系列营销“百事美食街”，</b></a>第一只短片是关于火锅的相亲故事，由周冬雨、张一山出演，这两位近期在广告片中的表现观众缘都不错。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=a0027ezt5ti\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p><b><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI2MzczNjc5NQ==&amp;mid=2247484354&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=21fd272fdc1a0e3437371ad57a16abbb&amp;chksm=eab61f76ddc1966097426dcb77cc3c4e6f1839f25e30e5cd819055baec7200925e315aa2c499&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=09051Emb77FeO1oOgbjzkczX&amp;key=bdb58425206827211ab13078001a9df5972b390598d43bbf51f50fdb81db55239337269e5e97818e36f3be2ee3605c6c9591638798d8e6257dbe488eafaee0cf1a1fae09eea90358390e4d5c1ab09c82&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MTIyNTYzODY0MA%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir6%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.13.6+build(17G65)&amp;version=11000006&amp;lang=zh_CN&amp;pass_ticket=DBE1%2B3MKLjg4wEFCe5vOnNvbEuIQTJRC17QhDTL5n5IcSGyx6hXevkKx6Qd8mVZa\" rel=\"nofollow\">9 月 12 日- 9 月 13 日，腾讯在深圳总部门前将开设一家只经营 48 小时的“微信情绪饮料”快闪店#WEMOTION#</a></b>，把人们日常交流中六种“微信情绪”，调制成了六款情绪饮料。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=y1347c7z0m2\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/36875.html?plat=ios&amp;from=singlemessage&amp;isappinstalled=0\" rel=\"nofollow\">领英联合瑞典旅游局、男人装等六个品牌，</a></b>做了一个惊奇职位贩卖机 H5，通过游戏给你推荐职位。<a href=\"https://h5.hecoe.com/pr/amazingjob2018/page/page.html\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里</a>试玩。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201809061117545A7XjiMQ2PFgRksE.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.461429\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906111809WNkMmZVeasOgGduh.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.461429\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>其他，也挺重要</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.thedrum.com/news/2018/09/05/beats-dr-dre-announces-global-partnership-with-nba-covering-marketing-and\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Beats 和 NBA 达成一项多年合作伙伴关系</b></a>，Beats 将从今年 10 月开始成为 NBA、WNBA 和 NBA G 联赛的音频合作伙伴。今年是 Beats 品牌成立十周年，将启用一系列 NBA 球星为其推广。</p><p><a href=\"https://www.mumbrella.asia/2018/09/ikea-names-wiedenkennedy-shanghai-as-creative-agency-in-china\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Wieden+Kennedy&nbsp;上海赢得了宜家（IKEA）中国地区的创意业务</b></a>。在今后的两年中，W+K上海将帮助宜家中国打造全国范围的整合营销及跨越数字、社交及零售的创意沟通。<br></p><p class=\"\"><br></p><p class=\"\">题图来源：<a rel=\"nofollow\" jsaction=\"mousedown:irc.rl;keydown:irc.rlk\" data-noload=\"\" target=\"_blank\" tabindex=\"0\" href=\"https://www.thenation.com/article/on-colin-kaepernicks-nike-ad-will-the-revolution-be-branded/\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwjyjLrAvKXdAhVbGTQIHaxPBzEQjB16BAgBEAQ\">The Nation</a></p>"}